{"tid":1385604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 罷工關鍵！第二擊！ 】 正式宣布802［公僕與市民］ 集會，市民將全力支援參與！","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:14:47.000Z","uid":287844,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca84696b4424a124653b20d1d651fa16e22bffd","tid":1385604,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">【 罷工關鍵！第二擊！ 】</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第一步 ：<br />\n8月2日嘅［公僕與市民］<br />\n罷工安全感集會！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解要咁多次醖讓罷工都唔成功？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為單一個人去罷，心理層面上面對 <br />\n孤立無援。要罷就一齊罷！齊上齊落！</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《公僕仝人，與民同行》集會<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><br />\n目標：&ldquo;致所有公僕、 車長、 市民 --- 8月5日罷工You'll never walk alone！&rdquo;，</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>哩枝<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">強心針</span></strong>係促成805大罷工嘅關鍵</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">日期：2019年8月2日（星期五）<br />\n<br />\n時間：晚上7 時至9時&nbsp;</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對象：公僕與[所有市民！]</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">地點：中環遮打花園</span><br />\n---------------------------------------------<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n8月2日嘅試水溫公務員集會<br />\n<br />\n個日晚一定要夠人去join，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不單止公務員，仲要call齊各界去，因為公務員數目有限，肯出黎巳經好大勇氣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋所有人都要企出黎保護翻佢哋。</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">原Post寫左<br />\n&rdquo;呼籲各公務員同事<strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">以及市民</span></strong></strong>一起參與這次集會。&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">市民都係重點，好多人以為哩個集會只for 公務員！所以要出大量文宣，話俾大家知一齊Join</span></strong>，</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">哩一晚，唔好淨係得公務員去集，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n市民將全力支援參加</span></span></strong>，請文宣幫手接力宣傳，互相比信心大家，相信大家，撐落去！！！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>安全感係關鍵！</strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">有咩你而家可以做：</span></strong><br />\n1. Like post<br />\n2. 推 Post<br />\n3.文宣組巴打出圖 加快宣傳力度<br />\n4. 叫齊身邊所有人參加802<br />\n5. Ig fb 開post 喚起所有溫層<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4c8b8746c5d468ea36b31392a56e5566f6af2384","tid":1385604,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cb9ebce7ac9e7d6f4d2240895841e595ae06ed","tid":1385604,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全力支援！！！"},{"pid":"b52c3c7a30f27ef30a7c6570f373c5f61071ae92","tid":1385604,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"<spa